238
00:14:47,094 --> 00:14:49,061
-Oh, I see.

239
00:14:49,095 --> 00:14:51,262
{\an1}That is noble of you.

240
00:14:51,296 --> 00:14:53,297
{\an1}That would be justice.

241
00:14:53,330 --> 00:14:57,498
{\an1}However, what about my family?

