00:14:57,531 --> 00:14:59,065
My friends?

243
00:14:59,099 --> 00:15:01,200
My village?

244
00:15:01,233 --> 00:15:03,234
{\an1}They suffered the same
fate of this village

245
00:15:03,267 --> 00:15:05,868
{\an1}at the hands of you
Hidden Leaf ninja.

246
00:15:05,901 --> 00:15:08,436
{\an1}How is it fair to let
only you people preach

247
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:09,635
{\an1}about peace and justice?

248
00:15:12,304 --> 00:15:14,171
{\an1}-What the hell are
