00:15:24,075 --> 00:15:26,377
{\an1}and profited from it.

253
00:15:26,410 --> 00:15:29,945
{\an1}Otherwise, the people of the
villages would've starved.

254
00:15:29,978 --> 00:15:32,679
{\an1}As it happened, our little
nation and its villages

255
00:15:32,712 --> 00:15:37,047
{\an1}became the battlefield where the
