259
00:15:54,587 --> 00:15:57,889
{\an1}You and I are both seeking
the very same thing.

260
00:15:57,922 --> 00:15:59,856
We both want to
achieve the peace

261
00:15:59,889 --> 00:16:02,758
{\an1}that Jiraiya-sensei envisioned.

262
00:16:02,791 --> 00:16:04,591
{\an1}You and I are the same.

263
00:16:04,624 --> 00:16:08,826
{\an1}We're both motivated by our
desire for peace and justice.

264
00:16:08,860 --> 00:16:10,527
