265
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:13,496
{\an1}against the Leaf village
is no different from what

266
00:16:13,528 --> 00:16:15,996
{\an1}you are trying to do to me.

267
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:20,731
{\an1}Everyone feels the same pain
when missing something dear.

268
00:16:20,765 --> 00:16:24,233
{\an1}You and I have both
experienced that pain.

269
00:16:24,266 --> 00:16:30,035
{\an1}You strive for your justice,
and I strive for mine.

270
00:16:30,068 --> 00:16:32,568
We're both just
ordinary men who have

271
00:16:32,602 --> 00:16:36,971
{\an1}been driven to seek vengeance
in the name of justice.

272
00:16:37,004 --> 00:16:40,205
{\an1}And, if one comes to
call vengeance justice,

273
00:16:40,239 --> 00:16:43,307
{\an1}such justice will only
breed further vengeance,

274
00:16:43,341 --> 00:16:48,642
{\an1}and trigger a vicious
cycle of hatred.

275
00:16:48,675 --> 00:16:52,411
{\an1}Right now, we live
in such a cycle.

276
00:16:52,444 --> 00:16:55,812
{\an1}I know the past, and
can foretell our future.

277
00:16:55,845 --> 00:16:58,846
{\an1}It is the same as our history.

278
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:02,281
{\an1}So we believe that human beings
simply cannot understand each

279
00:17:02,314 --> 00:17:04,215
{\an1}other, and they never will.

280
00:17:07,616 --> 00:17:11,651
{\an1}The shinobi world of ours is
ruled by hatred and hatred

