00:17:17,320 --> 00:17:17,787
-However.

283
00:17:20,688 --> 00:17:23,756
{\an1}Even I'm able to see that
there's entirely too much

284
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:26,791
{\an1}hate in this shinobi
world of ours.

285
00:17:26,824 --> 00:17:29,025
{\an1}-There's too much hate?

286
00:17:29,059 --> 00:17:30,526
{\an1}-I've always wanted
to do something

287
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:32,160
{\an1}about all of this hatred.

288
00:17:32,193 --> 00:17:35,961
{\an1}I'm just not quite sure
how to about it as of yet.

289
00:17:35,995 --> 00:17:39,063
{\an1}But I truly believe
that eventually, the day

290
00:17:39,096 --> 00:17:42,297
{\an1}will come when all people
