293
00:17:46,799 --> 00:17:49,500
{\an1}-And if I can't find the
solution to this problem,

294
00:17:49,534 --> 00:17:53,001
{\an1}then perhaps I'll entrust you
to find it instead, eh, Naruto?

295
00:17:53,034 --> 00:17:54,402
-Yes sir.

296
00:17:54,436 --> 00:17:57,203
{\an1}I can't turn down a request from
my master, can I, Pervy Sage?

297
00:18:00,504 --> 00:18:01,805
