298
00:18:01,838 --> 00:18:03,705
How would you
confront this hatred

299
00:18:03,739 --> 00:18:04,972
{\an1}in order to create peace?

300
00:18:09,774 --> 00:18:11,476
{\an1}I want to know what
your answer is.

301
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:24,247
-I don't know.

302
00:18:24,281 --> 00:18:25,881
{\an1}I don't have an answer.

303
00:18:34,018 --> 00:18:37,486
{\an1}-But you see, that is why
I formed the Akatsuki.

304
00:18:37,519 --> 00:18:40,253
{\an1}To break the cycle of hatred.

305
00:18:40,287 --> 00:18:42,054
{\an1}I can put an end to it.

306
00:18:42,088 --> 00:18:44,122
{\an1}But I need the Nine Tails.

307
00:18:44,155 --> 00:18:47,123
{\an1}I must have his power in
